lse,"comment_ctime":1629472445,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14514374333","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"我个人觉得 国内的很多公司，与其说是“管理”，不如说是“驱赶”。从来没有上司询问过个人的意愿，个人的发展目标之类的。只是单纯的拼命加班完成公司的KPI，或者以“晋升”&#47;“涨薪”作为管理工具。个人觉得，造成这种现象的，一方面是工程师红利，内卷；另一方面是资本的无序扩张，缺乏相应的法律法规作约束。","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":240567,"user_name":"何慧成","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2060270,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B7E076B1BEF1D5","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1596979001,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"14481880889","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"估计会在这里学习的，大部分都是工作狂居多。对于是否需要加班，还是以结果导向，一个是项目结果，另外一个是团队成长的结果。“没有功劳也有苦劳”这种评价方法要不得，也不要让下属产生这样的想法，形成不必要的、非正确导向的加班氛围。<br>但从国情来看，勤劳的中国人民应该大多数还是勤奋的，因此加班也不会少。","like_count":3,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1328734,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/46/5e/c0ea1ffb.jpg","nickname":"留白","note":"","ucode":"5267C1F3889961","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":402771,"discussion_content":"你说的很对","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1633946679,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":148783,"user_name":"mikejiang","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1396090,"ip_address":"","ucode":"9350F6DC7BC0E8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/15/4d/7a/106c3745.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1573086811,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10163021403","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"不加班就把事情搞定，公司搞成功的实在太少。在一定程度上，加班会推进项目的进度。很多时候，拼搏的时候压根就没有考虑到这是在加班，就想把事情搞定。","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":1465,"user_name":"GeekAmI","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1005030,"ip_address":"","ucode":"232C0B6DFB9F56","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/55/e6/87197b10.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1513176169,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10103110761","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"我们是创业公司，每个角色几乎都是一个人，没得选的...","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":1441,"user_name":"sylar5225","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1018530,"ip_address":"","ucode":"532E4545A33BB7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/8a/a2/9e7e60cb.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1513135336,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10103069928","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"很少遇到有一个良好的反馈体系的公司，和公司沟通到位不仅能够提升自己的主观能动性，对公司也是有很多促进作用，但很少有企业重视这些","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":1434,"user_name":"王建Tyrion","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1009595,"ip_address":"","ucode":"0A24883F0FB197","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/67/bb/abb7bfe3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1513126782,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10103061374","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"很有帮助啊","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":2493,"user_name":"赖晓强","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1028530,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5D7BC237FB55B2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b1/b2/0a71e6f1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1517442783,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"542","content":"写得很好","user_name":"池建强回复","user_name_real":"卖桃者","uid":"1000012","ctime":1517556066,"ip_address":"","comment_id":2493,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5812410079","product_id":100002401,"comment_content":"理想中的氛围和团队应该是，整体人性化一些，不强制，但是建立饱和度要求（一周加5小时？）。另外团队成员要有责任心，有想法，有目标，关键时候能打硬仗。这个在初期选人就很关键。年轻人（未婚无娃）时间更充裕一些，乐于探索和接触新技术，新方法，更有追求和冲劲，即使不在家也会继续学习，思考问题。","like_count":1,"